00:14:38.100 --> 00:14:39.530
So that's -- that's the connection.

00:14:39.530 --> 00:14:45.240
I think it has to do with -- with
numbers more than it does a sort

00:14:45.240 --> 00:14:51.570 position:56%
of binary connection that -- between
