00:22:34.310 --> 00:22:37.150
to hack DVDs, but it did
take that activity and put it

00:22:37.150 --> 00:22:39.220
at the fringes while leaving
a channel in the mainstream

00:22:39.220 --> 00:22:40.600
that helped to promote the --

00:22:40.600 --> 00:22:43.150
the availability of these
new business models.

00:22:43.150 --> 00:22:45.480
