get into the market for the --

00:23:07.240 --> 00:23:10.060
over-the-top television and
authenticated television

00:23:10.060 --> 00:23:14.000
to allow people to do streaming,
the DMCA has been a factor

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:16.460
in the willingness to engage
in all of those things.

00:23:16.460 --> 00:23:18.710
And so, I think it's --
from our perspective,

00:23:18.710 --> 00:23:22.480
has been both necessary
and successful.

