00:57:41.170 --> 00:57:42.620
Is that something that would --

00:57:42.620 --> 00:57:45.150
would strike the --
the proper balance?

00:57:45.150 --> 00:57:49.100
I'd be interested in
your thoughts about that.

00:57:49.100 --> 00:57:51.350
Mr. Zuck?

00:57:51.350 --> 00:57:52.650
