00:59:27.210 --> 00:59:28.510
&gt;&gt; Kevin Amer: Thank you.

00:59:28.510 --> 00:59:29.810
Mr. Panjwani?

00:59:29.810 --> 00:59:32.420
&gt;&gt; Raza Panjawani: A permanent
