01:00:08.300 --> 01:00:09.910
and I guess we're going to
go into this more with the --

01:00:09.910 --> 01:00:14.370
with the process panel -- involving
where is the appropriate balance

01:00:14.370 --> 01:00:17.190
between access for
fair use purposes,

01:00:17.190 --> 01:00:18.580
whether as a documentary filmmaker

01:00:18.580 --> 01:00:20.340
or narrative filmmaker
or an educator.

01:00:20.340 --> 01:00:25.320
And 1201 places a substantial
burden on those uses as well,

01:00:25.320 --> 01:00:29.260
not just those of embedded devices.

01:00:29.260 --> 01:00:32.740
And I would also caution
that any attempt

01:00:32.740 --> 01:00:34.770
to create a permanent exemption

01:00:34.770 --> 01:00:38.570
