01:00:51.350 --> 01:00:54.650
interest has been violated
but is the thing at dispute

01:00:54.650 --> 01:00:57.570
in this particular
litigation a device

01:00:57.570 --> 01:00:59.060
within the meaning of the statute.

01:00:59.060 --> 01:01:02.540
And that opens up a whole
can of worms, I think.

01:01:02.540 --> 01:01:03.840
&gt;&gt; Kevin Amer: Thank you.

01:01:03.840 --> 01:01:05.140
Mr. Pierre-Louis?

01:01:05.140 --> 01:01:06.610
&gt;&gt; Stan Pierre-Louis:
