manner of distribution now

01:01:45.540 --> 01:01:50.640
because consumers demand it and
our companies meet that demand.

01:01:50.640 --> 01:01:53.450
So we have to tread very carefully
as we think about what that means

01:01:53.450 --> 01:01:56.570
because it implicates more than
just thinking about a tractor.

01:01:56.570 --> 01:01:59.140
We're talking about the very
devices that consumers are using

01:01:59.140 --> 01:02:01.950
to consume the content
that we're making.

01:02:01.950 --> 01:02:03.250
&gt;&gt; Kevin Amer: Thank you.

