01:06:35.960 --> 01:06:37.260
with authentication, right.

01:06:37.260 --> 01:06:39.660
If you want to use a DVD
player, that drive has

01:06:39.660 --> 01:06:41.880
to authenticate itself to
ensure that it's playing

