cases has come out in a way

01:11:37.080 --> 01:11:40.030
that I think we all
agree was the right way.

01:11:40.030 --> 01:11:41.330
And -- and so, that seems

01:11:41.330 --> 01:11:43.750
to be a system that's
working, not one that's broken.

01:11:43.750 --> 01:11:46.880
And I -- I think that's --
we need to keep that in mind.

01:11:46.880 --> 01:11:49.360
I mean, I -- I -- as
a copyright owner,

01:11:49.360 --> 01:11:52.650
