answer being no, right?

01:11:56.100 --> 01:11:59.570
I -- there's this notion that,
wow, people are disincented

01:11:59.570 --> 01:12:02.550
to start new businesses that
might infringe copyright

01:12:02.550 --> 01:12:05.600
