01:12:05.600 --> 01:12:09.410
that this creative use of getting
around copyright law would be okay.

01:12:09.410 --> 01:12:13.530
And I think it's okay, instead,
that the default answer is no,

01:12:13.530 --> 01:12:14.830
which it is in most cases.

01:12:14.830 --> 01:12:17.330
It's not that confusing
what's legal and what isn't.

01:12:17.330 --> 01:12:21.410
And I think that we need to
look at the exceptions hard

01:12:21.410 --> 01:12:24.710
and then find a way to preserve
them into the future as a --

01:12:24.710 --> 01:12:28.660
as a better approach, I think,
than rejiggering the law.

