01:13:53.950 --> 01:13:57.250
as opposed to protecting
against copyright infringement,

01:13:57.250 --> 01:13:59.270 position:56%
I think what we say to the public is

01:13:59.270 --> 01:14:02.740
that market interests are more
important than the public safety

01:14:02.740 --> 01:14:05.930
or the potential public
health interests of ensuring

01:14:05.930 --> 01:14:11.610
that our increasingly connected
world is in fact secure.

01:14:11.610 --> 01:14:12.910
&gt;&gt; Kevin Amer: Thank you.

01:14:12.910 --> 01:14:15.240
